::DevilDuer/The Oblitercons/Firearm/Prowl::

DevilDuer growls as he sees Archangel run after the new femm.

"This is Alliance territory, Maximal," he says as he takes off also, 
firing his stun gun at Arcangel, "I suggest you get your skid plate 
out before I report this to Zardus and we crush you Maximals. That
bot 
belongs to us."

He activates his comm-link as he continues to fire. "Alliance troops, 
this is DevilDuer, I might need backup," he says into it.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Oblitertron roars once again as another charge hits him, seeing Prowl 
flying up near his arm. He swipes with his hand, trying to grab at
the 
Maximal.

"Prowl, watch out!" Firearm yelled, but it was too late.
Oblitertron's 
giant hand grabbed Prowl, ssmashing him into an equally giant fist. 
Oblitertron laughs as he releases Prowl's smashed body to fall toward 
the ground, recieving DevilDuer's transmission.

The huge bot turns around as Firearm catches Prowl, flying down to
the 
other Maximals. Oblitertron takes off at a run. The area that 
DevilDuer was at wasn't far, soon, he would be there....
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"Allright," Firearm says, landing near the others and seeing them 
complaining, "Everyone shut up, we need to get back to base. Alot of 
us need Medical attention."

He transforms into tank mode, tossing Prowl on his back. "I can carry 
one more, anyone need help to base?"
